170
00:10:50.859 --> 00:10:53.110
I got home late.
I don't know how late.

171
00:10:53.111 --> 00:10:55.572
Uh... She was already asleep.
Maybe midnight.

172
00:10:56.698 --> 00:10:58.657
She usually goes to bed
before... It doesn't matter.

173
